o e sulla città.</p><p>In un&rsquo;atmosfera suggestiva, gli ospiti gustano piatti stagionali preparati con cura e abilità. Quando fa caldo, il giardino invita a fermarsi all&rsquo;aria aperta.</p>','Bürgli','Bürgli','Bürgli','Bürgli','Saisonale Küche mit Blick auf den See und die Stadt.','Seasonal cuisine with a view of the lake and city.','Cuisine de saison avec vue sur le lac et la ville.','Cucina stagionale con vista sul lago e sulla città.',NULL,'https://cdn.zuerich.com/sites/default/files/web_zurich_restaurants_01.jpg',NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,'2020-02-23 13:30:25 +0100','Romantische Gartenterrasse','Romantic garden terrace','Terrasse de jardin romantique','Romantica terrazza fiorita',NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,'CH','Zürich',8038,'Kilchbergstrasse 15','+41 44 482 81 00','info@restaurantbuergli.ch','www.restaurantbuergli.ch',47.343092883289,8.533529475289,'<p>Montag bis Freitag, 09.00 &ndash; 24.00 Uhr<br />Samstag 18.00 &ndash; 24.00 Uhr<br />Sonntag 10.00 &ndash; 24.00 Uhr</p>','<p>Monday to Friday, 9.00am &ndash; 12.00am<br />Saturday 6.00pm &ndash; 12.00am<br />Sunday 10.00am &ndash; 12.00am</p>','<p>Du lundi au vendredi, 9h &ndash; 24h<br />Samedi 18h &ndash; 24h<br />Dimanche 10h &ndash; 24h</p>','<p>Da lunedì a venerdì, 9.00 &ndash; 24.00<br />Sabato 18.00 &ndash; 24.00<br />Domenica 10.00 &ndash; 24.00</p>','Monday,Tuesday,Wednesday,Thursday,Friday,Saturday,Sunday','POINT (47.343092883289 8.533529475289001)',2,'Restaurants in Zürich','Restaurants in Zurich','Restaurants à Zurich','Ristoranti a Zurigo'),
